#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_extract_lines
msgid "Extract Invoice Lines"
msgstr "Extraire les lignes de facturation"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_show_confidence
msgid "Confidence Indicators"
msgstr "Indicateurs de confiance"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_show_confidence
msgid "Each extracted field receives a reliability score (0.0 to 1.0) reflecting how confident the AI is about the value. Green = high confidence (>= 0.8), yellow = medium (>= 0.5), red = low (< 0.5). Useful to quickly spot fields that may need review."
msgstr "Chaque champ extrait reçoit un score de fiabilité (0.0 à 1.0) reflétant la certitude de l'IA sur la valeur. Vert = confiance élevée (>= 0.8), jaune = moyenne (>= 0.5), rouge = faible (< 0.5). Utile pour repérer rapidement les champs à vérifier."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_debug_mode
msgid "Detailed Logging"
msgstr "Journalisation détaillée"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_learning_enabled
msgid "Learning from Corrections"
msgstr "Apprentissage automatique"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_learning_enabled
msgid "When enabled, user corrections are recorded per vendor. After repeated identical corrections, the system applies them automatically on future invoices."
msgstr "Lorsqu'activé, les corrections utilisateur sont enregistrées par fournisseur. Après des corrections identiques répétées, le système les applique automatiquement sur les futures factures."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_auto_apply_threshold
msgid "Learning Threshold"
msgstr "Seuil d'apprentissage"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_auto_apply_threshold
msgid "Number of identical corrections needed before the system applies the correction automatically on future invoices."
msgstr "Nombre de corrections identiques nécessaires avant que le système applique automatiquement la correction sur les futures factures."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_cost_estimate
msgid "Estimated Cost per Invoice"
msgstr "Coût estimé par facture"

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_cost_estimate
msgid "Actual cost may vary depending on the document."
msgstr "Le coût réel peut varier en fonction du document."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_extract_lines
msgid "Without line extraction: one total line per invoice — the accountant allocates manually. Suited for simple invoices, uniform batches, or cost optimization.\nWith line extraction: description, quantity, price and tax per line. Suited for mixed-VAT invoices, multi-account allocation, and audit trail."
msgstr "Sans extraction de lignes : une seule ligne avec le total par facture — le comptable ventile manuellement. Adapté aux factures simples, lots uniformes, ou optimisation des coûts.\nAvec extraction de lignes : désignation, quantité, prix et taxe par ligne. Adapté aux factures multi-TVA, ventilation multi-comptes et audit trail."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_debug_mode
msgid "Creates an extraction log for each invoice processed, containing the full prompt sent to the AI, the raw response, token counts and estimated cost. Logs are accessible from the invoice form and from Invoicing > AI Dashboard > Extraction Logs."
msgstr "Crée un journal d'extraction pour chaque facture traitée, contenant le prompt complet envoyé à l'IA, la réponse brute, le nombre de tokens et le coût estimé. Les journaux sont accessibles depuis le formulaire facture et depuis Facturation > Tableau de bord IA > Journaux d'extraction."

#. module: account_invoice_digitize_ai
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_invoice_digitize_ai.field_res_config_settings__ai_auto_apply_threshold
msgid "When a user corrects an AI-extracted field, the correction is recorded per vendor. After this many identical corrections for the same field and vendor, the system applies the correction automatically on future invoices. Set to 0 to disable learning."
msgstr "Lorsqu'un utilisateur corrige un champ extrait par l'IA, la correction est enregistrée par fournisseur. Après ce nombre de corrections identiques pour le même champ et fournisseur, le système applique la correction automatiquement sur les futures factures. Mettre à 0 pour désactiver l'apprentissage."

